install OpenCV 2.4.8 as it is the newest version of ubuntu in which released on 31 Dec 2013

# source:
-source file: http://opencv.org/downloads.html
-install direction: http://karytech.blogspot.co.uk/2012/05/opencv-24-on-ubuntu-1204.html

# installation steps
-Install Dependencies
-Compile and Install 
-Testing

# note: in "Compile and Install" step

-cmake option need to be changed to 
<cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RELEASE -D CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local ..>

-skip doing last two minor-steps which are "/usr/local/lib" and "sudo ldconfig"






